{
  "stem": "14060.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But generally speaking, all I can say is that on that 19th of March, which was a Sunday in 1944, I got up from a comfortable bed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I look out the window.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And because we were literally a kilometer from the border, at about 8:30 or 8:00, I see German military walking past.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were not in tanks or trucks or anything.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They were just walking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They were walking in, in, in lines of four, just one line of four people next to each other, which took up half of the road-- not the pavement, on the road.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that is the way how they sort of announced their presence.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "This was the, the visual impression which we got.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And I realized that everybody got terribly worried and upset and telephoning left right and center, this is happening, that's happening.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And then within days the machinery started.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "As I told you, my uncle got arrested, and the Judenrat got appointed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "Everybody had to report any details.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Lists and lists were made.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "The Germans dictated to the Judenrat, which they dutifully carried out by quickly registering every person who attended the feat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And so they knew where the Jews were, not that it could not have been eventually found out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "But strangely enough, the Jews contributed-- OK, maybe under certain threat-- to be good boys and give everything to them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And if we give them that, everything will be all right.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "This is not what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Anyway, coming to the point of the deportation because I have told you that we were a few days in this brick building, which had no windows.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Food was not even available very much, just very little.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in the ghetto, strange enough, we were-- we were lacking somewhat the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
